    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="用ufw替代iptables">用ufw替代iptables</h1><figure class="highlight groovy"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd ~</span><br><span class="line">wget <span class="string">https:</span><span class="comment">//launchpad.net/ufw/0.33/0.33/+download/ufw-0.33.tar.gz</span></span><br><span class="line">tar zxvf ufw-<span class="number">0.33</span>.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">cd ufw-<span class="number">0.33</span></span><br><span class="line">python ./setup.py install</span><br><span class="line">chmod -R g-w <span class="regexp">/etc/</span>ufw <span class="regexp">/lib/</span>ufw <span class="regexp">/etc/</span><span class="keyword">default</span><span class="regexp">/ufw /</span>usr<span class="regexp">/sbin/</span>ufw</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>安装完后查看ufw是否启动了<code>ufw status</code>，是inactive的情况下进行如下操作。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ufw <span class="operator"><span class="keyword">reset</span></span><br><span class="line">ufw <span class="keyword">default</span> deny</span><br><span class="line">ufw <span class="keyword">allow</span> <span class="number">22</span></span><br><span class="line">ufw <span class="keyword">allow</span> <span class="number">80</span></span><br><span class="line">ufw <span class="keyword">allow</span> <span class="number">443</span></span><br><span class="line">ufw <span class="keyword">allow</span> <span class="number">21</span></span><br><span class="line">ufw <span class="keyword">allow</span> <span class="number">60000</span>:<span class="number">60099</span>/tcp</span><br><span class="line">ufw <span class="keyword">allow</span> <span class="number">943</span></span><br><span class="line">ufw <span class="keyword">allow</span> <span class="number">1194</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ufw <span class="keyword">enable</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>22是ssh，80是http，443是https，21是ftp，<code>60000:60099/tcp</code>是ftp over tls时设置的port域，943和1194是openvpn。<br>其他的port根据需要自己再添加。</p>
<h5 id="打开log转发">打开log转发</h5><p>创建<code>vi /etc/rsyslog.d/20-ufw.conf</code>，内容如下</p>
<figure class="highlight applescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">:msg,<span class="keyword">contains</span>,<span class="string">"[UFW "</span> /var/<span class="command">log</span>/ufw.<span class="command">log</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>重启 rsyslog service</p>
<figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title">service</span> rsyslog restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后就可以看到log出现在 <code>/var/log/ufw.log</code>，很多攻击信息的。</p>
]]></content>
